OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wed 15 Apr to Fri 24 Apr
OL,6,FChangeable at the start of this period
OL,7,Fwith low pressure to the west or
OL,8,Fnorthwest of the UK. This will bring
OL,9,Fshowers or longer spells of rain at
OL,10,Ftimes, heaviest and most persistent in
OL,11,Fthe northwest together with some
OL,12,Fstrong winds. The southeast is likely
OL,13,Fto be driest and brightest. Later,
OL,14,Fconditions may become drier and more
OL,15,Fsettled, especially in the north, but
OL,16,Fparts of the south may still see some
OL,17,Fshowers or longer spells of rain.
OL,18,FTemperatures will likely be near to or
OL,19,Fslightly above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
