OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 24 Apr to Fri 8 MayFThe
OL,6,Fdominant pattern during this period is
OL,7,Fmost likely to be high pressure to the
OL,8,Fnorth and lower pressure to the south.
OL,9,FThis will probably lead to the driest,
OL,10,Fmost settled weather in the north of
OL,11,Fthe UK, with the south more unsettled
OL,12,Fand wetter. Temperatures will probably
OL,13,Fclose to or slightly above normal
OL,14,Foverall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
